<tr><td>Mana:</td>
<td>35</td></tr>
<tr><td>Skill:</td>
<td>Alteration</td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top>
Classes:</td>
<td>
<a href="/spells/enchanter.shtml">
Enchanter</a>
 (8)<BR>
</td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top>Items:</td>
<td>
<a href="/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml#rod_of_insidious_glamour">Rod of Insidious Glamour</a><br>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>Buyable:</td><td>
Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>Researchable:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Drops from MOB:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Cast Time:</td>
<td>3.50 seconds</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><br></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>Description:</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
Increases your faction rating with target by 100 points.</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
<BR>1 tick = 6 seconds<BR>
When a range of effects are given, it usually means that the effect becomes more potent as the caster increases in levels.
</td></tr>
