<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>no one will EVER attack you for casting this upon them and the spell is not resistable.<BR>
it increases faction with the npc by 100 points (the equivelant of killing 100 goblins)<BR>
this spell is a MUST for quests. cast it on the npc before doing the quest or asking for a quest. if the quest had a variable item it gives you it will increase your chances of getting a better item as the npc usually gives you better items as faction increases. <BR>
casting this spell on a merchant will not affect prices in any way<BR>
hope this helps<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
kalzan<BR>
